msgctxt "56_Tanimura"
msgid "Chief, I have a few things I need to check out. Why don't I see you later?"
msgstr "Chief, I have a few things I need to check out. Why don't I see you later?"

msgctxt "68_Hisai"
msgid "That's fine. I'll be back at the station if you need me."
msgstr "That's fine. I'll be back at the station if you need me."

msgctxt "80_Hisai"
msgid "Just don't do anything crazy, you hear? Your father wouldn't want you going out guns blazing over this."
msgstr "Just don't do anything crazy, you hear? Your father wouldn't want you going out guns blazing over this."

msgctxt "92_Tanimura"
msgid "I wouldn't go that far..."
msgstr "I wouldn't go that far..."

msgctxt "116_Tanimura"
msgid "(I think I'll head back to <Color:7>Homeland<Color:Default> for now. I need some time to digest all this.)"
msgstr "(I think I'll head back to <Color:7>Homeland<Color:Default> for now. I need some time to digest all this.)"

